---
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tejendra Singh Danu | Full Stack Developer</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Portfolio of Tejendra Singh Danu — a full stack developer focused on scalable applications, modern frontends, and dependable backends." />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <nav class="container nav">
        <a class="brand" href="#home">Tejendra Singh Danu</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="#about">About</a>
          <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
          <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main id="home">
      <section class="hero container">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">Full Stack Developer • .NET, React, Cloud</p>
          <h1>Building resilient products from API to interface.</h1>
          <p class="hero-text">
            I create dependable web applications and services that balance performance, scalability, and a thoughtful user experience.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#projects">See Selected Work</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#contact">Start a Conversation</a>
          </div>
          <ul class="hero-highlights">
            <li>End-to-end delivery from planning through deployment</li>
            <li>Modern frontend experiences with React and TypeScript</li>
            <li>Robust backend services built with .NET and cloud-native tooling</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card" aria-label="Professional overview">
          <div class="avatar">TD</div>
          <h3>Focused on building practical, high-impact systems.</h3>
          <p>From clean architecture to polished interfaces, I enjoy turning complex requirements into reliable solutions.</p>
          <div class="hero-metrics">
            <div>
              <strong>5+</strong>
              <span>Years in production delivery</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>20+</strong>
              <span>Projects shipped end to end</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-chips">
            <span>.NET</span>
            <span>React</span>
            <span>Azure</span>
            <span>Docker</span>
            <span>SQL</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="about" class="section container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
          <h2>I turn complex ideas into dependable products with clarity and care.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-copy">
            <p>I’m a full stack developer who enjoys building products that are as reliable in production as they are pleasant to use.</p>
            <p>My work spans backend architecture, modern frontend interfaces, database design, and cloud deployment, always with an emphasis on maintainability and measurable impact.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-highlights">
            <div class="highlight-card">
              <h3>Architecture</h3>
              <p>Designing scalable services and APIs with clear boundaries and long-term maintainability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
              <h3>Performance</h3>
              <p>Improving responsiveness, efficiency, and resilience across applications and integrations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
              <h3>Delivery</h3>
              <p>Shipping polished solutions through thoughtful collaboration, testing, and practical iteration.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="skills" class="section section-alt">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <p class="eyebrow">Skills</p>
            <h2>Core strengths across the modern web stack.</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="skills-grid">
            <article class="card skill-card">
              <span class="card-icon">01</span>
              <h3>Frontend</h3>
              <p>React, TypeScript, responsive UI, component-driven development, and design system thinking.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card skill-card">
              <span class="card-icon">02</span>
              <h3>Backend</h3>
              <p>.NET, ASP.NET, REST APIs, authentication, data modeling, and service-oriented architecture.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card skill-card">
              <span class="card-icon">03</span>
              <h3>Operations</h3>
              <p>AWS, Docker, CI/CD, Git, monitoring, and deployment automation for production systems.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="projects" class="section container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Selected Projects</p>
          <h2>Work shaped by clarity, craft, and measurable product value.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="projects-grid">
          <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-preview preview-one"></div>
            <h3>Enterprise Portal Platform</h3>
            <p>Built secure, multi-tenant workflows with performant APIs and a streamlined operations experience.</p>
            <div class="tags"><span>.NET</span><span>React</span><span>SQL</span></div>
          </article>
          <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-preview preview-two"></div>
            <h3>Analytics Dashboard</h3>
            <p>Designed a modern reporting experience that made complex data easier to interpret and act on.</p>
            <div class="tags"><span>TypeScript</span><span>UI</span><span>API</span></div>
          </article>
          <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-preview preview-three"></div>
            <h3>Cloud-Native Service</h3>
            <p>Delivered a scalable service layer with containerized deployment and automation across environments.</p>
            <div class="tags"><span>Docker</span><span>AWS</span><span>CI/CD</span></div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" class="section section-alt">
        <div class="container contact-card">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
            <h2>Let’s build something meaningful together.</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:hello@tejendradanu.dev">Email Me</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#home">Back to Top</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="container footer-content">
        <p>© <span id="year"></span> Tejendra Singh Danu. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/script.js" is:inline></script>
  </body>
</html>
